      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) مَنْ أَتَى ذَاتَ مَحْرَمٍ ضُرِبَ ضَرْبَةً بِالسَّيْفِ أَخَذَتْ مِنْهُ مَا أَخَذَتْ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Asbat, from Abdullah Bin Bukeyr, from his father who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The one who comes to a <span class=\"iTxt\">Mahram</span> would be struck with a strike of the sword, taking from him what it takes (lives or dies)’."
        ]
      }
